      <title>LG能源与WesCEF签署第二份协议以扩大锂供应</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-signs-2nd-agreement-with-wescef-expand-lithium-supply-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国 LG Energy Solution 周二与澳大利亚 Wesfarmers Chemicals、Energy and Fertilizers (WesCEF) 签署了第二份承购协议，以扩大其锂采购供应链。]]></description>
